#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:553
msgid "Cell statistics"
msgstr "Cellstatistik"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:555
msgid ""
"Computes per-cell statistics based on input raster layers and for each cell "
"writes the resulting statistics to an output raster. At each cell location, "
"the output value is defined as a function of all overlaid cell values of the"
" input rasters."
msgstr ""
"Beräknar statistik per cell baserat på ingående rasterlager och för varje "
"cell skrivs den resulterande statistiken till ett utdataraster. På varje "
"cellplats definieras utdatavärdet som en funktion av alla överlagrade "
"cellvärden i indatarastren."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:560
msgid ""
"By default, a NoData cell in ANY of the input layers will result in a NoData"
" cell in the output raster. If the :guilabel:`Ignore NoData values` option "
"is checked, then NoData inputs will be ignored in the statistic calculation."
" This may result in NoData output for locations where all cells are NoData."
msgstr ""
"Som standard kommer en NoData-cell i NÅGOT av inmatningslagren att resultera"
" i en NoData-cell i utdatarastret. Om alternativet :guilabel:`Ignore NoData "
"values` är markerat ignoreras NoData-ingångar i den statistiska beräkningen."
" Detta kan resultera i NoData-utdata för platser där alla celler är NoData."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:566
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Reference layer` parameter specifies an existing raster layer"
" to use as a reference when creating the output raster. The output raster "
"will have the same extent, CRS, and pixel dimensions as this layer."
msgstr ""
"Parametern :guilabel:`Reference layer` anger ett befintligt rasterlager som "
"ska användas som referens när utdatarastern skapas. Utdatarastret kommer att"
" ha samma utsträckning, CRS och pixeldimensioner som detta lager."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:571
msgid ""
"**Calculation details:** Input raster layers that do not match the cell size"
" of the reference raster layer will be resampled using ``nearest neighbor "
"resampling``. The output raster data type will be set to the most complex "
"data type present in the input datasets except when using the functions "
"``Mean``, ``Standard deviation`` and ``Variance`` (data type is always "
"``Float32`` or ``Float64`` depending on input float type) or ``Count`` and "
"``Variety`` (data type is always ``Int32``)."
msgstr ""
"**Beräkningsdetaljer:** Rasterlager i indata som inte matchar cellstorleken "
"i referensrasterlagret kommer att omsamplas med hjälp av ``närmaste granne "
"omsampling``. Rasterdatatypen för utdata sätts till den mest komplexa "
"datatypen i indatasetet, utom när funktionerna ``Mean``, "
"``Standardavvikelse`` och ``Varians`` används (datatypen är alltid "
"``Float32`` eller ``Float64`` beroende på indatatyp) eller ``Count`` och "
"``Variety`` (datatypen är alltid ``Int32``)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:580
msgid ""
"``Count``: The count statistic will always result in the number of cells "
"without NoData values at the current cell location."
msgstr ""
"``Count``: Count-statistiken resulterar alltid i antalet celler utan NoData-"
"värden på den aktuella cellpositionen."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:583
msgid ""
"``Median``: If the number of input layers is even, the median will be "
"calculated as the arithmetic mean of the two middle values of the ordered "
"cell input values."
msgstr ""
"``Median``: Om antalet inmatningslager är jämnt beräknas medianen som det "
"aritmetiska medelvärdet av de två mellersta värdena i de ordnade "
"cellinmatningsvärdena."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:586
msgid ""
"``Minority/Majority``: If no unique minority or majority could be found, the"
" result is NoData, except all input cell values are equal."
msgstr ""
"``Minoritet/Majoritet``: Om ingen unik minoritet eller majoritet kunde "
"hittas, blir resultatet NoData, förutom att alla indatacellvärden är lika."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:593
msgid ""
"Example with all the statistic functions. ``NoData`` cells (grey) are taken "
"into account."
msgstr ""
"Exempel med alla statistiska funktioner. ``NoData``-celler (grå) tas med i "
"beräkningen."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:613
msgid "Input raster layers"
msgstr "Inmatade rasterlager"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:614
msgid "**Statistic**"
msgstr "**Statistik**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:615
msgid "``STATISTIC``"
msgstr "``STATISTIC``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:619
msgid "Available statistics. Options:"
msgstr "Tillgänglig statistik. Alternativ:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:621
msgid "0 --- Sum"
msgstr "0 --- Summa"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:622
msgid "1 --- Count"
msgstr "1 --- Räkning"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:623
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:4342
msgid "2 --- Mean"
msgstr "2 --- Medelvärde"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:624
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:4343
msgid "3 --- Median"
msgstr "3 --- Median"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:625
msgid "4 --- Standard deviation"
msgstr "4 --- Standardavvikelse"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:626
msgid "5 --- Variance"
msgstr "5 --- Avvikelse"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:627
msgid "6 --- Minimum"
msgstr "6 --- Minimum"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:628
msgid "7 --- Maximum"
msgstr "7 --- Maximalt"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:629
msgid "8 --- Minority (least common value)"
msgstr "8 --- Minoritet (minsta gemensamma värde)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:630
msgid "9 --- Majority (most common value)"
msgstr "9 --- Majoritet (vanligaste värdet)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:631
msgid "10 --- Range (max - min)"
msgstr "10 --- Område (max - min)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:632
msgid "11 --- Variety (unique value count)"
msgstr "11 --- Variety (antal unika värden)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:638
msgid ""
"Calculate statistics also for all cells stacks, ignoring NoData occurrence."
msgstr ""
